original_title: Chikara: Kid's Eat Free On Tuesday
overview: The fourth graduating class from the Wrestle Factory begin to debut here! Shane Storm arrives, and teams with Private Eye! Jigsaw begins to jockey for position as a contender to the Mike Quackenbush's I-CROWN. An innovative trios match serves as the main event!
title: Chikara: Kid's Eat Free On Tuesday
